---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="" id="intro">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Robert brings <span class="gradient-text">15+ years</span> of drumming to the
    table. <br />
    Classically trained in <span class="text-primary">jazz</span> and <span
      class="text-primary">rock</span
    >, rooted in contemporary <span class="text-primary">Christian worship</span
    >, and skilled in <span class="text-primary">metalcore</span>.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="mailto:robert@rochadrums.com?subject=rochadrums request"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="email" class="h-8" />
      <span>Contact</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="#services"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="magnify" class="h-8" />
      <span>Keep reading...</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
